               <text>
                  <paragraph>GENTAK<sup>®</sup> Gentamicin sulfate ophthalmic ointment USP, 0.3% is supplied in 3.5 g tube, box of one. </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>(NDC 63187-873-35) </paragraph>
               </text>
