                     <code code="44425-7" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="STORAGE AND HANDLING SECTION"/>
                     <text>
                        <paragraph>
                           <content styleCode="bold">STORAGE:</content> Store at 2° to 30°C (36° to 86°F). </paragraph>
                        <paragraph>
                           <content styleCode="bold">Akorn</content>
                           <br/>Manufactured by: Akorn, Inc.<br/>Lake Forest, IL 60045</paragraph>
